        <object label="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Product Attributes&lt;/b&gt;" Description="Describes essential properties or characteristics of the product, such as dimensions, weight, color, or material specifications." Role="Enables detailed product descriptions that support quality control, functionality, and compatibility checks during design and manufacturing." id="7iJxjdkOMapWwhl0Z6aH-1806">
