        <object label="&lt;font&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lifecycle Stages&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" Description="Specifies different stages of the product lifecycle, including design, manufacturing, distribution, and disposal." Role="Lifecycle stages provide a roadmap for product development and management, ensuring each phase aligns with overall goals and sustainability considerations." id="7iJxjdkOMapWwhl0Z6aH-1810">
