        <object label="Parametric Design Ontology" Description="Parametric design ontology organizes knowledge around parameters and constraints that guide the generation of designs. It includes the definition of variables, dependencies, and rules that dynamically control design outputs, enabling the creation of adaptable and responsive forms." Id="303" References="" placeholders="1" Role="It focuses on the interplay between variables, setting it apart from other ontologies by emphasizing flexibility through parameters rather than static shapes or structures." id="Z8ZMG5t9qmk1xCjCsyjZ-1994">
